nodes.text: Dorak Quinn was a male Human hunter whom Revan met in Anchorhead during the Jedi Civil War. In 3956 BBY, he was one of the newer hunters on Tatooine. Dorak was, at first, rude to Revan when he met him in Fazza's Hunting Lodge. Quinn later developed respect for the reformed Sith Lord upon learning that Revan, along with fellow hunter Komad Fortuna, had killed a Krayt dragon in the Dune Sea.
